---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import FooterNL from '../../../components/FooterNL.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Gearfreak | zomeren.studio"
  description="Gearfreak brand identity case study by Marco van Zomeren for WADM."
  lang="nl"
  enPath="/projects/gearfreak/"
  nlPath="/nl/projects/gearfreak/"
  ogImage="https://zomeren.studio/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/1_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp"
  bodyClass="project-page"
  schema={`{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"CreativeWork","name":"Gearfreak | zomeren.studio","description":"Gearfreak brand identity case study by Marco van Zomeren for WADM.","url":"https://zomeren.studio/nl/projects/gearfreak/","inLanguage":"nl-NL","isPartOf":{"@type":"WebSite","name":"zomeren.studio","url":"https://zomeren.studio/"}}`}
>
  <Header enHref="/projects/gearfreak/" nlHref="/nl/projects/gearfreak/" lang="nl" />
  <main class="pb-24 md:pb-36">
    <section data-reveal>
      <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/1_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak cover" class="project-featured-image aspect-[16/9] w-full object-cover" />
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-14 md:px-12 md:pt-20">
      <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,5.4vw,5.2rem)] leading-[0.97] tracking-[-0.02em]">Gearfreak</h1>
          <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-6 text-[clamp(1rem,1.5vw,2rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.01em]">
            <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">What</p>
            <p>Brand identity</p>
            <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">Where</p>
            <p>WADM</p>
            <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">Role</p>
            <p>Designer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7">
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.05vw,2.8rem)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.012em]">
            GearFreak, a surf and outdoor sports retailer, wanted to sharpen its brand to better connect its webshop, physical store, and sports clinics. Over the years, the company built a loyal local community, but its communication lacked consistency and emotional impact. Through the BrainSells&reg; Spark program, WADM redefined the brand from the inside out&mdash;clarifying its story, personality, and positioning. The goal: strengthen the GearFreak brand experience across every touchpoint, from online shopping to hands-on lessons, and stand out in a competitive outdoor sports market.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-14 md:px-12 md:pt-20">
      <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        <video class="aspect-video w-full object-cover" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/zomerenstudio/video/upload/v1762721536/gearfreak_1920x1080_cxjaaa.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-16 md:px-12 md:pt-24">
      <div class="space-y-10 md:space-y-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,1.35vw,1.7rem)] uppercase leading-none tracking-[0.04em] lg:col-span-2">Design</p>
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.05vw,2.8rem)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.012em] lg:col-span-8 lg:col-start-5">
            The new identity builds on the idea &ldquo;Experience our expertise&rdquo;&mdash;linking the team&rsquo;s technical know-how to the thrill of wind, water, and snow. WADM developed a design system that balances professional confidence with human warmth: a clear tone of voice, bold typography (Mona Sans and Manrope), natural and energetic photography, and a modern color palette rooted in the outdoor experience. The refreshed visuals and messaging connect the webshop, shop floor, and surf clinics into one unified and recognizable brand experience.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,1.35vw,1.7rem)] uppercase leading-none tracking-[0.04em] lg:col-span-2">Result</p>
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.05vw,2.8rem)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.012em] lg:col-span-8 lg:col-start-5">
            With a sharper story and consistent visual system, GearFreak now presents itself as a brand driven by expertise and enthusiasm. The renewed identity enhances both customer trust online and the sense of community in-store and during clinics. Supported by a tactical communication plan&mdash;covering website, social media, and on-location materials&mdash;the new GearFreak brand now stands stronger, clearer, and ready for growth.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-14 md:px-12 md:pt-20">
      <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/2_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 2" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/3_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 3" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/4_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 4" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/5_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 5" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/6_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 6" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/7_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 7" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/8_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 8" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/9_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 9" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/10_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 10" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/11_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 11" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/12_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 12" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/13_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 13" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/14_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 14" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/15_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 15" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/16_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 16" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/17_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 17" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/18_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 18" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/19_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak image 19" class="w-full object-cover" />
